SED editor
===========
strealine editor, non-interactive

create the line
update the line
delete the line

it add temporarly in runtime
sed 'li Hello SED' <filename>

if you want add in the acutal file you use -i
sed -i '1i hello' <filename> ->insert after first line
sed 'la hello' ->insert after first line
sed '2d' -> delete second line
sed '/hello/d' -> delete lines where hello present
sed 's/root/Root/' ->subsititute first occurences in every line
sed 's/sbin/SBIN/g' ->substitute gobally means in all lines
sed '3c/ change' ->replaces the line
sed '/error/ c NO-ERROR -> change the line based on pattern

idempotent
==========
Scripts should give same results even you run them infinite times is called idempotency

GET -> Idempotent
POST -> chance of duplicates or error.. we need work for idempotency
PUT/UPDATE -> not danger, check if already same then dont allow chnage
DELETE -> not danger, but check if already deleted, then tell it is deleted already

CHECK roboshop user already exist or not, if exit skip otherwise create

mongosh mongodb.rdaws86s.fun --quiet --eval
"db.getCollectionNames().includes('COLLECTION_NAME')"


instead of using validate() function use set to reduce number of lines in script

trap command in shell
